        " قَالَ اَلنَّبِيُّ صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ : \"اَلْوَلاَءُ لُحْمَةٌ كَلُحْمَةِ اَلنَّسَبِ، لاَ تُبَاعُ وَ لاَ تُوهَبُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3494 - Isma'il ibn Muslim narrated from Imam Jafar ibn Muhammad Al-Sadiq (as) from his father, Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as), who said:\nThe Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him and his family, said:\n\"Wala' (the bond of loyalty) is like the bond of lineage; it cannot be sold or given away as a gift.\""
        ]
      }
